short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirect any contest page in Codeforces to the standings containing only Brazilian participants.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension filters the standings for a given contest on Codeforces to show only Brazilian competitors.
